lx-0's PUBLIC plugin catalog for Claude Code and Cursor. Hosts bundle
plugins under `./plugins/<name>/`, standalone skills under
`./skills/<category>/<slug>/`, and lists external plugins via marketplace.json.

---

## Listed plugins

Each bundled / standalone plugin in this repo carries its own LICENSE and
description. Where present, plugin-level NOTICE files document additional
attribution. Unless stated otherwise, all plugins are MIT licensed.

External plugins are referenced via the marketplace.json `plugins[]` array.
This catalog does NOT redistribute external plugin source -- Claude Code /
Cursor fetch them directly from the upstream repo at install time.

See `.compiled/marketplace.json` for the authoritative list (regenerated by
`node compile.mjs` from `./marketplace.json` + auto-discovered bundles +
standalone).

---

## Claude Code and Cursor

This repo serves a marketplace.json compatible with Claude Code (a product of
Anthropic, <https://claude.com/code>) and Cursor (<https://cursor.com>). The
marketplace and plugin formats are part of those products' public extension
APIs.
